abstract: Quotation of the Day for Saturday, December 21, 2019.

lead_paragraph: “You have police, F.B.I., judges, prosecutors, defense attorneys, hours and hours of work undone on the whim of one person. It’s almost like a godlike power.”

abstract: Even with Gordon Hayward out of the lineup and Kemba Walker having a tough shooting night, the Boston Celtics had more than enough offense against the struggling Detroit Pistons.

abstract: Mexico has extradited a son of drug lord Ismael "El Mayo" Zambada to the United States to face trial on narcotics trafficking charges, a government official and media reports said on Friday.
snippet: Mexico has extradited a son of drug lord Ismael "El Mayo" Zambada to the United States to face trial on narcotics trafficking charges, a government official and media reports said on Friday.
lead_paragraph: MEXICO CITY — Mexico has extradited a son of drug lord Ismael "El Mayo" Zambada to the United States to face trial on narcotics trafficking charges, a government official and media reports said on Friday.
headline_main: Son of Mexican Kingpin Zambada Extradited to U.S. to Face Trial
headline_print_headline: Son of Mexican Kingpin Zambada Extradited to U.S. to Face Trial

abstract: Stef Smith had 20 points as Vermont romped past Lipscomb 86-63 on Friday night.

abstract: The Floyd County sheriff said that several of the horses were pregnant, and that the killing was probably premeditated.
snippet: The Floyd County sheriff said that several of the horses were pregnant, and that the killing was probably premeditated.
lead_paragraph: The crime scene — deep in Appalachia’s coal country — is so desolate that the only way in or out is by all-terrain vehicle. There are no paved roads to speak of.
